OL,3,CRare 'roll cloud' amazes beachgoers
OL,4,Cand weather experts in Portugal
OL,6,FPictures show a huge roll of clouds
OL,7,Fcoming from the ocean and closer to
OL,8,Fthe beach.
OL,10,FPortugal like much of Europe has been
OL,11,Fexperiencing a heatwave in recent
OL,12,Fdays, but another rare weather
OL,13,Fphenomenon also gripped many
OL,14,Fbeachgoers trying to survive the warm
OL,15,Ftemperatures by the sea.
OL,17,FOn Sunday, across some parts of the
OL,18,Fnorthern and central Coast of
OL,19,FPortugal, a 'roll cloud', as it is
OL,20,Fcommonly referred to, was seen and
OL,21,Frecorded by many.
