OL,3,CRare 'roll cloud' amazes beachgoers
OL,4,Cand weather experts in Portugal
OL,6,FThe continuous formation of big
OL,7,Fdimensions is simply a cloud, even if
OL,8,Fits impressive size and shape make for
OL,9,Fa scary scene.
OL,11,FAccording to climate expert Mario
OL,12,FMarques, the occurrence of the
OL,13,Fformation is not a first in Portugal
OL,14,Fbut it is a more common in places such
OL,15,Fas Australia.
