OL,6,FIt happens more often there due to
OL,7,FTasmania's colder air coming in
OL,8,Fcontact with contrasting high
OL,9,Ftemperatures, according to Marques.
OL,11,FHe said the phenomenon is usually
OL,12,Fquite quick.
