OL,3,CRare 'roll cloud' amazes beachgoers
OL,4,Cand weather experts in Portugal
OL,6,FHe said: "It is a process of formation
OL,7,Fof cloudiness very quick, fleeting,
OL,8,Fthat disappears very quickly but that
OL,9,Fhas its beauty. It's a tubular
OL,10,Fformation, shaped as a tube, that for
OL,11,Fthose who have never seen it may cause
OL,12,Fsome fear but there is no reason for
OL,13,Fthat because it's nothing more than a
OL,14,Fcloud."
