OL,3,CRare 'roll cloud' amazes beachgoers
OL,4,Cand weather experts in Portugal
OL,6,FTiago Pinho, a beachgoer in Figueira
OL,7,Fda Foz with an interest in these rare
OL,8,Fphenomenon said that he saw the cloud
OL,9,Fcoming and got ready to film, but
OL,10,Fpeople around him were not so
OL,11,Fknowledgeable of what was happening
OL,12,Fand it became tense with some
OL,13,Fpanicking.
OL,15,FA bit further north, Rui Fernandes
OL,16,Fwitnessed the same cloud formation and
OL,17,Fthe panic of some people.
