OL,3,CRare 'roll cloud' amazes beachgoers
OL,4,Cand weather experts in Portugal
OL,6,FMarques explained that for the cloud
OL,7,Fto form a certain set of conditions of
OL,8,Fwind, temperatures and humidity need
OL,9,Fto be in place.
OL,11,FHe said: "During the day and during
OL,12,Fthese hot days the surface of the land
OL,13,Fis warm and we have hot air at the
OL,14,Fsurface, but when the sun begins to
OL,15,Fset if we have an intrusion of cold
OL,16,Fair, because it is heavier and more
OL,17,Fdense, it begins to replace the hot
OL,18,Fair and the hot air begins to rise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
