OL,3,CRare 'roll cloud' amazes beachgoers
OL,4,Cand weather experts in Portugal
OL,6,F"That's why we have this formation
OL,7,Falways by the water, rolling up, not
OL,8,Fmoving, as if there is a hot air wall."
OL,10,FOn Monday, Portuguese weather service
OL,11,FIPMA confirmed the rare occurrence
OL,12,Fwith a satellite image.
OL,14,FIt said the formation had begun in the
OL,15,Fafternoon approaching mainland
OL,16,FPortugal from the west, between
OL,17,FPeniche and Povoa do Varzim around 5pm
OL,18,Fand 6pm local time.
